<H1>Debian French Pages</H1>

<H2>French user mailing list</H2>

<P>This list is the place to ask your questions about Debian in French.

<P>To subscribe, send a message to 
<A href="mailto:debian-user-french-request@lists.debian.org">
debian-user-french-request@lists.debian.org</A>
with
<BLOCKQUOTE>
      <CODE>subscribe <var>&lt;your_email_address&gt;</var></CODE>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
in the body (not in the subject).

<H2>French news mailing list</H2>

<P>This list offers announces and news about the Debian project in French.

<P>To subscribe, send a message to 
<A href="mailto:debian-news-french-request@lists.debian.org">
debian-news-french-request@lists.debian.org</A>
with
<BLOCKQUOTE>
      <CODE>subscribe <var>&lt;your_email_address&gt;</var></CODE>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
in the body (not in the subject).

<H2>Translation project</H2>

<P>
This project consists of translating www.debian.org,
Debian documents and specific Debian software (for example the 
installation process) into French.
 
<P>
This project is coordinated by Denis Barbier &lt;barbier@debian.org&gt;,
and Martin Quinson &lt;mquinson@ens-lyon.fr&gt; (Christophe Le Bars
used to act as a coordinator in the past)
and the preferred media for it is the 
<A HREF="mailto:debian-l10n-french@lists.debian.org">
<I>debian-l10n-french</I></A> mailing list.

<P>
See also the <a href="french/index.fr.html">project web site</a> for more
information.

<H2>French developer mailing list</H2>

<P>The <A href="mailto:debian-devel-french@lists.debian.org">
debian-devel-french@lists.debian.org</A>
list is dedicated to discussions in French about Debian related
development issues.

